sql:
SELECT product_id
FROM product_updates
WHERE new_price < old_price;

SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity
FROM orders
WHERE account_id = 1;

SELECT SUM(o.total_amount) AS total_sales 
FROM orders o
WHERE o.sales_rep_id NOT IN (
  SELECT t.sales_rep_id 
  FROM sales_targets t
);

external_knowledge:
- 'treasures' refers to distinct products (product_id); 
- 'lone sales guardian' refers to a sales representative with ID 0; 
- 'eastern realm' refers to the region with ID 1.
